module.exports = {

  crc8: require('./crc8'),

  crc16: require('./crc16'),
  crc16ccitt: require('./crc16ccitt'),
  crc16modbus: require('./crc16modbus'),
  crc16xmodem: require('./crc16xmodem'),
  crc16kermit: require('./crc16kermit'),
  crc24: require('./crc24'),
  crc32: require('./crc32'),
